<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>saltstack on 南寨小子</title><link>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/tags/saltstack/</link><description>Recent content in saltstack on 南寨小子</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 17 Jun 2017 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://kangxiaoning.github.io/tags/saltstack/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>saltstack源码分析-publisher</title><link>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/post/2017/06/master-publisher/</link><pubDate>Sat, 17 Jun 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/post/2017/06/master-publisher/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="1-原理">1. 原理&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>saltstack默认利用zeromq进行消息传递。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>salt-master启动时会执行如下操作&lt;/p>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>以PUB模式监听在&amp;rsquo;tcp://{interface}:{publish_port}'&lt;/li>
&lt;li>以PULL模式监听在&amp;rsquo;ipc://opts[&amp;lsquo;sock_dir&amp;rsquo;]/publish_pull.ipc'&lt;/li>
&lt;li>publish_pull.ipc在while True循环中运行，一旦有消息进来就调用pub_sock.send(payload)发送消息&lt;/li>
&lt;li>minion会connect到publish_port，因此一旦有消息，所有minion都会收到&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>extending-saltstack读书笔记</title><link>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/post/2017/04/extending-saltstack-notes/</link><pubDate>Fri, 07 Apr 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://kangxiaoning.github.io/post/2017/04/extending-saltstack-notes/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="1-双下划线开始和结尾的object">1. 双下划线开始和结尾的object&lt;/h1>
